│ From this log, I identified the first transformation point as:              │
│                                                                             │
│ ```                                                                         │
│ llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineCompares.cpp::canonicalizeICmpBo │
│ ol()                                                                        │
│ ```                                                                         │
│                                                                             │
│ Here is the relevant backtrace at the moment of the transformation:         │
│                                                                             │
│ ```stack                                                                    │
│ (frame 1) llvm/lib/Transforms/InstCombine/InstCombineCompares.cpp:7182 in   │
│ canonicalizeICmpBool                                                        │
